Morocco,Q3s8L_fjHjU,Ugwt2Tt7_k3-a2L168F4AaABAg,,@artdirector9517,"This video is marvel👌. Yeah Kingdom of Moroccoo is such a mix of flavors. it's stuning as package and his landscapes is incredibley diverse. Sahara desert, oasis, woods, snow, rivers, two water front long Atlantic Ocean and Mediterranean Sea, surf spots, mountains, colorful towns, old medina, vibrant souks, festivals and much more. He has too a rich culture of food, music, hand craft, traditionnel clothing, home furnitur, interior design, tiles etc.. As you can see in Marrakech city as berber saharien or in Tanger as mauresque with some spanish archetecture touch, the city that contains the world's first United States embassy in the history. Also kingdom of Morocco is the first country to recognize USA in the world at 1777. We are so open as civilisation for exemple about the spanish influences, they were in the north of Morocco for almost 50 yeras but not problem becaus we were in their country for 800 years 😊 that's pretty much isn't ?! lool. We left the last city Grenada at january of 1492, Just a few month later, they discovered America at october of 92 by Columbus using our tools. they translated too our books left in the university of Cordoba the best university in the world at that time. Two years after Spain become the new bigest super power on earth with Portugal. Why not ?! nothing was missing 🙂. Just for information it's the empire of Morocco who built almost 60 % of spanish cities. for exemple Garnata city become Grenada, Ichbillia city become Sevilla, kortoba become Cordoba, Balancia become Valencia etc.. It's so easy isn't ! 😎 as it is for the 40 other cities. All this legacy of sciences has crossed borders of the Andalousie reached France then to England and Florence city in Italy by Sicily island to declare the edge of renaissance in europe. For information, the oldest university in the world called Al-Qarawiyyin in Fez city and while there were 400 Hamam (public bath) in Sevilla city and oil-powered lamp-posts in her streets there were any one in Paris or London. Also kingdom of Morocco is the oldest kingdom systeme in the world with japan .Any way we are brothers every one of us carries the torch of progress. For reference, Steve Jobs' father is Syrian but the most signifiant of all this is the first traveler in the history and the first who draw a map of the planet earth were too moroccans, They are Ibn Battuta and Al-Idrissi. So strange isn't ?! 🤔 especialy it was a right map even without satellite 😅. Any way last time Morocco become the hidden paradise of surfers, motobikers, caravaners, stylists, artists, photographers, Retirees overseas and digital nomades 🤫. Joy it as you can, life is too short than you. think. Hey, nice video 👍 keep going 🙏 .'''..'''..'' '.''.. '.'''.''",2026-03-13T03:42:17Z,2026-03-13T03:42:17Z,2,False,4.0,2026-05-15T02:01:00.130063
