Casablanca,yG-lKxPb5yU,Ugy4lv2OJxMQtsUKU514AaABAg.ARxcm6wlNGdAU7dgO5mdAc,Ugy4lv2OJxMQtsUKU514AaABAg,@gemanscombe4985,"Rick wasn't helping Victor and Ilsa until she explained her train station no-show. He finally got that, then had to get Victor out of Captain Reynaud's custody and set up the pair's clean getaway. Rick realized that him and Ilsa having the hots for each other paled beside the importance of Victor's mission, and that staying together in Casablanca was impossibly dangerous. The script writers made sure Rick didn't have any easy outs, just a tough one.",2026-03-09T09:19:08Z,2026-03-09T09:24:23Z,0,True,,2026-05-15T02:01:18.884792
