Marrakech,YRzBoL2qhp8,UgzK3VrwyNC7sJnIyH14AaABAg.A9nNM3zhgtJA9riVohpmfM,UgzK3VrwyNC7sJnIyH14AaABAg,@ReigneOrShine,"Thanks for watching! We walked everywhere in Marrakech, but we visited the Jardin Majorelle on our last day in the city at the end of the whole Morocco trip. We were coming back to Marrakech from Casablanca by train, so we stayed one last night in a different hotel called Hotel Racine, which is closer to the train station and to the Jardin Majorelle, so we walked from there instead. From the Riad Dreams you would need to walk 30 minutes to the Jardin Majorelle, so we would advise to get a taxi (always agree the price before entering the vehicle) if you stay there and want to visit the gardens. Have a lovely trip!",2024-10-21T17:06:17Z,2024-10-21T17:06:17Z,1,True,,2026-05-15T02:01:48.850381
