Marrakech,05QDGvi0_sM,UgwvIJpx2CEQO27dNhV4AaABAg.AAxHm7YfzdWAAzM1kyUXj8,UgwvIJpx2CEQO27dNhV4AaABAg,@FindingGinaMarie,"Hi @NicolasDudic-ph4kd! Thank you so much for watching and for your kind comment. We appreciate it. Have you seen our full series from Morocco, which includes a Sahara Desert tour and our 18 days in Fes, which we really loved? I'll put a link below if you are interested.—Judy
