Tourism,wFZyNQAIcdE,UgxLAX0YaAE7P7syo0p4AaABAg,,@WizardOfOss,"Lol.....so most of the most popular tourist destinations are....overly touristy? Who would have thought.....

In the end, most of these places are so popular for a good reason. I mean, have you really been to Paris or New York if you avoided the Eiffel Tower or Times Square? Just keep your expectations realistic, and don't plan any trip just around such hotspots, but give yourself time to explore less touristy places. I have been to a couple of these 20 places (one even multiple times!), and don't regret visiting any of them.",2026-05-07T15:27:32Z,2026-05-07T15:27:32Z,0,False,0.0,2026-05-15T02:02:20.241021
