Tourism,tcGjKt8XRTI,Ugxa_69EcIS0uNAe9zl4AaABAg,,@Cobbmtngirl,"I visited Amsterdam many many years ago and had such a great time. I was amazed at the sites and the people. I do remember being in the red light district and seeing signs specifically telling people not to take pictures. And of course, there’s an American peeking around the corner with his camera taking pictures. So many tourists that behave badly ruin it for those that respect it all. It’s very sad.",2026-05-06T16:32:35Z,2026-05-06T16:33:23Z,0,False,0.0,2026-05-15T02:02:24.568066
